== Chinese ==
===Etymology===
[[自行]] ''zì xíng'' (done by oneself) + 车 ''chē''(vehicle)

===Pronunciation===
====Mandarin====
*Pinyin: [[zì xíng chē]]

===Noun===
'''[[自]][[行]][[车]]''' (simplified characters)

#bicycle

====Synonyms====
[[脚踏车]] jiǎotàchē (used in Taiwan)

